[[
Use my DVD drive (recommended)

- This technique helps you install Tails on a flash memory (USB stick or SD card) through burning a DVD
  first.
- You need: 1 DVD and 1 flash memory (USB stick or SD card of at least 4 GB)
|install/mac/dvd-usb]]

[[
Use only flash memories

- This technique helps you install Tails on a flash memory (USB stick or SD card) by using a temporary
  Tails on a second flash memory.
- It requires using the command line.
- You need: 2 flash memories (USB sticks or SD cards of at least 4 GB)
|install/mac/usb]]
